column2: select objID, clean, u, g, r, i , z, u_err, g_err, r_err, i_err, z_err, ra, dec, ra_err, dec_err, RowNumber from (select s.objID, s.clean, s.psfMag_u - s.extinction_u as u, s.psfMag_g - s.extinction_g as g, s.psfMag_r - s.extinction_R as r, s.psfMag_i - s.extinction_i as i, s.psfMag_z - s.extinction_z as z, s.psfMagErr_u as u_err, s.psfMagErr_g as g_err, s.psfMagErr_r as r_err, s.psfMagErr_i as i_err, s.psfMagErr_z as z_err, s.ra, s.dec, s.raErr as ra_err, s.decErr as dec_err, ROW_NUMBER () over (order by s.dec) as RowNumber from star as s) as OS where OS.RowNumber % # = # AND OS.CLEAN = # AND OS.ra BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.dec BETWEEN # AND # AND OS.psfMag_r < # AND OS.psfMag_g < #
